==Gameplay Notes==
===Special Mechanics===
* Able to perform OASW at 100 ASW.
* Able to equip Daihatsu and Type 2 Ka-Mi tank at Kai Ni.

===Overview===
'''Kai'''
* Average firepower, torpedo, ASW, HP and armour.  

'''Kai Ni'''
* Good firepower and torpedo.
* Average ASW and HP.
* Decent armour.

